@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Created
Created --> Processing : reject
Processing --> Approved : approve
Processing : entry / log book
Approved --> Rejected : submit
Approved : entry / log book
Rejected --> Archived : approve
Archived --> Closed : submit
Approved --> Rejected : revert
Closed --> [*]
@enduml